        "chapter": 23,
        "line_start": 98,
        "line_end": 98,
        "text": "村中尽是断垣残壁，甚为破败"
      },
      {
        "chapter": 24,
        "line_start": 76,
        "line_end": 78,
        "text": "十九年之前，我来过这里的"
      }
